                          Core.Response - Shared Codes

Core.Response deals with LSPDFR and provides additional shared code and tools
for WithLithum's LSPDFR plugins.

It is devired from RelaperCommons.

Dependencies

    Place 'LSPD First Response.dll' in the 'blobs' folder. You can also carry
    the XML file.

    All other dependencies are resolved automatically through NuGet.